# NeuroStock Platform Upgrade — Walkthrough

## What Was Done

### 🔧 Backend (`src/`)

| File | Change |
|---|---|
| [app.py](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/PROJECTS/stock_market%20prediction/src/app.py) | Added `/market-overview`, `/compare`, `/watchlist-prices` endpoints |
| [sentiment.py](file:///c:/Users/FARAZ%20KHAN/Desktop/DEKSTOP/PROJECTS/stock_market%20prediction/src/sentiment.py) | Added live RSI calculation + trend direction (`bullish`/`bearish`/`neutral`) via `yfinance` |

### ⚛️ Frontend (`frontend/src/`)

**New Files**
| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `context/WatchlistContext.jsx` | Global watchlist state with `localStorage` persistence |
| `components/NavBar.jsx` | Sticky top nav with logo, links, watchlist badge |
| `components/MarketOverviewBar.jsx` | Scrolling live ticker bar (SPY, QQQ, DIA, BTC-USD…) |
| `pages/WatchlistPage.jsx` | `/watchlist` — shows starred stocks with live prices |
| `pages/ComparePage.jsx` | `/compare` — side-by-side prediction chart for 2 tickers |

**Modified Files**
| File | Change |
|---|---|
| `App.jsx` | Added `WatchlistProvider`, `NavBar`, `MarketOverviewBar`, star button, new routes |
| `components/Background.jsx` | Changed particles from pink → neon-blue; added radial glow overlay |
| `components/StatsCard.jsx` | Color-coded borders, bottom glow accent line on hover, arrow icons |
| `components/StockInput.jsx` | Added AAPL/TSLA/NVDA/MSFT/AMZN quick-select pills |
| `components/SentimentGauge.jsx` | Dynamic arc color, glowing needle, RSI badge, trend direction badge |
| `components/PredictionChart.jsx` | Volume bar sub-chart, legend row |
| `index.css` | `@keyframes marquee` for ticker bar, glow-pulse, cleaner scrollbar |

