> [!NOTE]
> The Market Overview Bar requires the Flask backend to be running on port 5000. Start it with `.venv\Scripts\activate` then `python src/app.py` from the project root.

---

## How to Start

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Backend
cd "c:\Users\FARAZ KHAN\Desktop\DEKSTOP\PROJECTS\stock_market prediction"
.venv\Scripts\activate
python src/app.py

# Terminal 2 — Frontend
cd frontend
npm run dev
```

Open **http://localhost:5173**
